# Golden snapshot directory — populated on first Linux CI run.
#
# Phase 3e sub-cluster D (T3e.8/T3e.9) byte-compares ReceiptGenerator output to
# the .golden.pdf / .golden.png files committed here. SkiaSharp rasterisation
# differs across platforms, so goldens are gated to Linux CI per the CLAUDE.md
# hard rule. Tests Skip on macOS / Windows; on Linux a missing golden fails the
# test with a regen instruction.
